Syntax: punch <target>

Delivers a standard punch to an opponent. Punch is a basic Pugilist-line
unarmed attack skill handled by the Warrior attack system. It is one of
the foundational unarmed techniques and is available to most combat classes
that train unarmed fighting.

Requirements:
  - Must be in combat or initiates combat on the target.
  - Target must be present in the room.
  - Must have the skill learned.

See also: shelp punch pummel aurabolt palmstrike kick
